Package rbvs.record

Class Invoice

  • java.lang.Object
    • rbvs.record.Record
      • rbvs.record.Invoice
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IInvoice
    public class Invoice
extends Record
implements IInvoice
    Provides the implementation for the IInvoice interface and extends the class Record. It is associated with a PaymentTransaction and a list of IShoppingCartElements. In essence, it provides the means to encapsulate a PaymentTransaction with a list of IShoppingCartElements.
    Author:
    OOP
